Place avocados, cilantro, lemon juice, salt, onion powder, and white pepper in a blender container or food processor bowl. Add chicken broth; cover and blend or process until smooth. Transfer to a glass bowl. Stir in 1 cup LACTAID(R) Reduced Fat Milk. Cover and refrigerate for at least 3 hours or up to 8 hours. Stir before serving. Season to taste with additional salt and white pepper. If necessary, stir in additional LACTAID(R) Reduced Fat Milk to reach desired consistency. Garnish with lemon slices, if desired.